<div dir="ltr">I have a build of OMPI 1.7.4rc2r30031 on FreeBSD-9 finally.<div>I can (as I will detail in another email) run only singletons at the moment.</div><div>However, when I do I get a warning that is, IMHO, unnecessary:</div>
<div><br></div><div><div><font face="courier new, monospace">$ mpirun -np 1 examples/ring_c</font></div><div><font face="courier new, monospace">--------------------------------------------------------------------------</font></div>
