<div><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif">The warning is correct that no such interface exists.</font></div><div><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif">However <a href="http://127.0.0.1/24">127.0.0.1/24</a> DOES exist:</font></div>
<div><div style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><br></div><div><font face="courier new, monospace" size="1">$ ifconfig lo0 inet</font></div><div><font face="courier new, monospace" size="1">lo0: flags=8049&lt;UP,LOOPBACK,RUNNING,MULTICAST&gt; metric 0 mtu 16384</font></div>
