<div style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><br></div></div><div><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif">I&#39;ve confirmed that if_include and if_exclude have default values (not my fault):</font></div>
<div><div><font face="courier new, monospace" size="1">$ ompi_info --param btl tcp           </font></div><div><font face="courier new, monospace" size="1">                 MCA btl: parameter &quot;btl_tcp_if_include&quot; (current value: &quot;&quot;,</font></div>
